        <body>
            <entry xml:id="entry_arm" xml:lang="os">
                <form xml:id="form_d2060e66" xml:lang="os-x-iron" type="lemma"><orth>arm</orth></form>
                <form xml:id="form_d2060e69" xml:lang="os-x-digor" type="dialectal"><orth>ar(m)</orth></form>
                <sense n="1" xml:id="sense_arm.1"><abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                        <q>рука</q>
                    </abv:tr><abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                        <q>hand</q>
                    </abv:tr></sense>
                <sense n="2" xml:id="sense_arm.2"><abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                        <q>оглобля</q>
                    </abv:tr><abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                        <q>shaft</q>
                    </abv:tr></sense>
                <re xml:id="re_d2060e92">
                    <note type="comment" xml:lang="ru">в иронском в самостоятельном употреблении
                        также встречается реже, чем <hi rendition="#rend_italic">kʼūx</hi>, но в сложных словах, пословицах,
                        речениях, идиоматических выражениях преобладает <hi rendition="#rend_italic">arm</hi> (совершенно так же,
                        как в аналогичных случаях <ref type="xr" target="#entry_fad"/> преобладает
                        над <ref type="xr" target="#entry_kʼax"/> ‘нога’, а <ref type="xr" target="#entry_kom"/> — над <ref type="xr" target="#entry_ʒyx"/> ‘рот’):
                        ср.</note>
                    <note type="comment" xml:lang="en">in Iron, in independent use it is also less
                        common than <hi rendition="#rend_italic">kʼūx</hi>, but <hi rendition="#rend_italic">arm</hi> prevails in compound words, sayings, set
                        phrases and idiomatic expressions (exactly the same way as in analogous
                        cases <ref type="xr" target="#entry_fad"/> prevails over <ref type="xr" target="#entry_kʼax"/> ‘foot’, and <ref type="xr" target="#entry_kom"/>
                        prevails over <ref type="xr" target="#entry_ʒyx"/> ‘mouth’): cf.</note>
                    <re xml:id="re_d2060e116" xml:lang="os-x-iron">
                        <lang/>
                        <form xml:id="form_d2060e120" type="lemma"><orth>ærxūd</orth></form>
                        <sense xml:id="sense_d2060e123"><abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                                <q>перчатка</q>
                            </abv:tr><note type="comment" xml:lang="ru"> („шапка руки“)</note><note type="comment" xml:lang="en"> (‘hat of the hand’)</note><abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                                <q>glove</q>
                            </abv:tr><note type="comment" xml:lang="ru"> („шапка руки“)</note><note type="comment" xml:lang="en"> (‘hat of the hand’)</note><note type="comment" xml:lang="ru">(из <hi rendition="#rend_italic">ærm-xūd</hi>) </note><note type="comment" xml:lang="en">(from <hi rendition="#rend_italic">ærmxūd</hi>) </note></sense>
                    </re>
                    <re xml:id="re_d2060e146">
                        <form xml:id="form_d2060e148" type="lemma"><orth>ærmkʼūx</orth></form>
                        <sense xml:id="sense_d2060e151"><def xml:lang="ru">id.</def><def xml:lang="en">id.</def></sense>
                    </re>
                    <re xml:id="re_d2060e158" xml:lang="os-x-iron">
                        <lang/>
                        <form xml:id="form_d2060e162" type="lemma"><orth>æmʒæǧd</orth></form>
                        <sense xml:id="sense_d2060e165"><abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                                <q>отбивание такта при танце</q>
                            </abv:tr><abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                                <q>beating the beat while dancing</q>
                            </abv:tr><note type="comment" xml:lang="ru">(из <hi rendition="#rend_italic">ærm-ʒæǧd</hi>)
                                </note><note type="comment" xml:lang="en">(from <hi rendition="#rend_italic">ærmʒæǧd</hi>)
                            </note></sense>
                    </re>
                    <re xml:id="re_d2060e181" xml:lang="os-x-digor">
                        <lang/>
                        <form xml:id="form_d2060e185" type="lemma"><orth>ærʒæf</orth></form>
                        <sense xml:id="sense_d2060e188"><def xml:lang="ru">id.</def><def xml:lang="en">id.</def><note type="comment" xml:lang="ru">(из <hi rendition="#rend_italic">ærmʒæf</hi>) </note><note type="comment" xml:lang="en">(from <hi rendition="#rend_italic">ærmʒæf</hi>) </note></sense>
                    </re>
                    <re xml:id="re_d2060e199" xml:lang="os-x-iron">
                        <lang/>
                        <form xml:id="form_d2060e203" type="lemma"><orth>ævdasarm</orth></form>
                        <sense xml:id="sense_d2060e206"><abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                                <q>передняя ляжка животного</q>
                            </abv:tr><abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                                <q>front thigh of an animal</q>
                            </abv:tr></sense>
                    </re>
                    <re xml:id="re_d2060e217" xml:lang="os-x-digor">
                        <lang/>
                        <form xml:id="form_d2060e221" type="lemma"><orth>cavdar</orth></form>
                        <sense xml:id="sense_d2060e224"><def xml:lang="ru">id.</def><def xml:lang="en">id.</def><note type="comment" xml:lang="ru">(← <hi rendition="#rend_italic">cavd-arm</hi>) </note><note type="comment" xml:lang="en">(← <hi rendition="#rend_italic">cavd-arm</hi>) </note></sense>
                    </re>
                    <re xml:id="re_d2060e235" xml:lang="os-x-digor">
                        <lang/>
                        <form xml:id="form_d2060e239" type="lemma"><orth>kʼoxar</orth></form>
                        <sense xml:id="sense_d2060e242"><abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                                <q>весло</q>
                            </abv:tr><abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                                <q>paddle</q>
                            </abv:tr></sense>
                    </re>
                    <re xml:id="re_d2060e253">
                        <form xml:id="form_d2060e255" type="lemma"><orth>armyʒag</orth></form>
                        <sense xml:id="sense_d2060e258"><abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                                <q>горсть</q>
                            </abv:tr><abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                                <q>handful</q>
                            </abv:tr></sense>
                    </re>
                    <re xml:id="re_d2060e269" xml:lang="os-x-iron">
                        <lang/>
                        <form xml:id="form_d2060e273" type="lemma"><orth>ʒagarm</orth></form>
                        <sense xml:id="sense_d2060e276"><abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                                <q>с полными руками</q>
                            </abv:tr><abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                                <q>will full hands</q>
                            </abv:tr></sense>
                    </re>
                    <re xml:id="re_d2060e288" xml:lang="os-x-iron">
                        <lang/>
                        <form xml:id="form_d2060e292" type="lemma"><orth>armytʼæpæn</orth></form>
                        <sense xml:id="sense_d2060e295"><abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                                <q>ладонь</q>
                            </abv:tr><abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                                <q>palm</q>
                            </abv:tr></sense>
                    </re>
                    <re xml:id="re_d2060e306" xml:lang="os-x-iron">
                        <lang/>
                        <form xml:id="form_d2060e310" type="lemma"><orth>dælarm</orth></form>
                        <sense xml:id="sense_d2060e313"><abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                                <q>под мышкой</q>
                            </abv:tr><abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                                <q>under one's arm</q>
                            </abv:tr></sense>
                    </re>
                    <re xml:id="re_d2060e324" xml:lang="os-x-iron">
                        <lang/>
                        <form xml:id="form_d2060e328" type="lemma"><orth>æmarmæj</orth></form>
                        <sense xml:id="sense_d2060e331"><sense xml:id="sense_d2060e332"><abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                                    <q>дружно</q>
                                </abv:tr><abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                                    <q>together</q>
                                </abv:tr></sense><sense xml:id="sense_d2060e341"><abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                                    <q>разом</q>
                                </abv:tr><abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                                    <q>at the same time</q>
                                </abv:tr></sense></sense>
                    </re>
                    <re xml:id="re_d2060e352">
                        <form xml:id="form_d2060e354" type="lemma"><orth>ærmæftæw</orth></form>
                        <sense xml:id="sense_d2060e357"><sense xml:id="sense_d2060e358"><abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                                    <q>мешочек</q>
                                </abv:tr><abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                                    <q>small bag</q>
                                </abv:tr></sense><sense xml:id="sense_d2060e367"><abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                                    <q>переметная сумка</q>
                                </abv:tr><abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                                    <q>weather-vane</q>
                                </abv:tr></sense></sense>
                    </re>
                    <re xml:id="re_d2060e378" xml:lang="os-x-iron">
                        <lang/>
                        <form xml:id="form_d2060e382" type="lemma"><orth>ælmærin</orth></form>
                        <sense xml:id="sense_d2060e385"><abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                                <q>локоть (мера)</q>
                            </abv:tr><abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                                <q>cubit</q>
                            </abv:tr></sense>
                    </re>
                    <re xml:id="re_d2060e396">
                        <form xml:id="form_d2060e398" type="lemma"><orth>ræmbyn</orth></form>
                        <sense xml:id="sense_d2060e401"><abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                                <q>локоть</q>
                            </abv:tr><abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                                <q>elbow</q>
                            </abv:tr><note type="comment" xml:lang="ru">(из <hi rendition="#rend_italic">ærmbyn</hi>) </note><note type="comment" xml:lang="en">(from <hi rendition="#rend_italic">ærmbyn</hi>) </note></sense>
                    </re>
                    <re xml:id="re_d2060e417" xml:lang="os-x-iron">
                        <lang/>
                        <form xml:id="form_d2060e421" type="lemma"><orth>ærmǧ˳yroj</orth></form>
                        <sense xml:id="sense_d2060e424"><abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                                <q>ручная мельница</q>
                            </abv:tr><abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                                <q>handmill</q>
                            </abv:tr></sense>
                    </re>
                    <re xml:id="re_d2060e435">
                        <form xml:id="form_d2060e437" type="lemma"><orth>ærmæg</orth></form>
                        <sense xml:id="sense_d2060e440"><abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                                <q>материал</q>
                            </abv:tr><abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                                <q>material</q>
                            </abv:tr></sense>
                    </re>
                    <re xml:id="re_d2060e451">
                        <form xml:id="form_d2060e453" type="lemma"><orth>ærmæǵy</orth></form>
                        <sense xml:id="sense_d2060e456"><abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                                <q>наличными</q>
                            </abv:tr><abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                                <q>in cash</q>
                            </abv:tr></sense>
                    </re>
                    <re xml:id="re_d2060e467">
                        <form xml:id="form_d2060e469" type="lemma"><orth>ældar</orth></form>
                        <sense xml:id="sense_d2060e472"><sense xml:id="sense_d2060e473"><abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                                    <q>владетель</q>
                                </abv:tr><abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                                    <q>possessor</q>
                                </abv:tr></sense><sense xml:id="sense_d2060e482"><abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                                    <q>князь</q>
                                </abv:tr><abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                                    <q>prince</q>
                                </abv:tr></sense><note type="comment" xml:lang="ru">(← <hi rendition="#rend_italic">ærm-dar</hi>)
                                </note><note type="comment" xml:lang="en">(← <hi rendition="#rend_italic">ærm-dar</hi>)
                            </note></sense>
                    </re>
                    <re xml:id="re_d2060e497" xml:lang="os-x-iron">
                        <lang/>
                        <form xml:id="form_d2060e501" type="lemma"><orth>ærmaræxst</orth></form>
                        <sense xml:id="sense_d2060e504"><abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                                <q>искусный</q>
                            </abv:tr><abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                                <q>skilled</q>
                            </abv:tr></sense>
                    </re>
                    <re xml:id="re_d2060e515" xml:lang="os-x-iron">
                        <lang/>
                        <form xml:id="form_d2060e519" type="lemma"><orth>ærmax˳yr</orth></form>
                        <sense xml:id="sense_d2060e522"><abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                                <q>прирученный</q>
                            </abv:tr><abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                                <q>tamed</q>
                            </abv:tr></sense>
                    </re>
                    <re xml:id="re_d2060e534" xml:lang="os-x-iron">
                        <lang/>
                        <form xml:id="form_d2060e538" type="lemma"><orth>ærmærmi</orth></form>
                        <sense xml:id="sense_d2060e541"><abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                                <q>с рук на руки</q>
                            </abv:tr><abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                                <q>from hand to hand</q>
                            </abv:tr></sense>
                    </re>
                    <re xml:id="re_d2060e552" xml:lang="os-x-iron">
                        <lang/>
                        <form xml:id="form_d2060e556" type="lemma"><orth>armæj qazyn</orth></form>
                        <sense xml:id="sense_d2060e559"><abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                                <q>баловаться руками</q>
                            </abv:tr><abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                                <q>do sth with hands</q>
                            </abv:tr></sense>
                    </re>
                    <re xml:id="re_d2060e570" xml:lang="os-x-iron">
                        <lang/>
                        <form xml:id="form_d2060e574" type="lemma"><orth>armæj ævnalyn</orth></form>
                        <sense xml:id="sense_d2060e577"><abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                                <q>трогать руками</q>
                            </abv:tr><abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                                <q>touch with hands</q>
                            </abv:tr></sense>
                    </re>
                    <re xml:id="re_d2060e588" xml:lang="os-x-iron">
                        <lang/>
                        <form xml:id="form_d2060e592" type="lemma"><orth>armaccagæj cævyn</orth></form>
                        <sense xml:id="sense_d2060e595"><abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                                <q>бить передними ногами (о лошади)</q>
                            </abv:tr><abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                                <q>beat with front legs (about a horse)</q>
                            </abv:tr></sense>
                    </re>
                    <re xml:id="re_d2060e606" xml:lang="os-x-iron">
                        <lang/>
                        <form xml:id="form_d2060e610" type="lemma"><orth>ærmydūltæ kænyn</orth></form>
                        <sense xml:id="sense_d2060e613"><sense xml:id="sense_d2060e614"><abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                                    <q>мять в руках</q>
                                </abv:tr><abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                                    <q>fumble</q>
                                </abv:tr></sense><sense xml:id="sense_d2060e623"><abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                                    <q>уродовать</q>
                                </abv:tr><abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                                    <q>disfigure</q>
                                </abv:tr></sense></sense>
                    </re>
                    <re xml:id="re_d2060e634" xml:lang="os-x-iron">
                        <lang/>
                        <form xml:id="form_d2060e638" type="lemma"><orth>mæ army nīcy īs</orth></form>
                        <sense xml:id="sense_d2060e641"><abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                                <q>не располагаю средствами</q>
                            </abv:tr><abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                                <q>I don't have the funds</q>
                            </abv:tr></sense>
                    </re>
                    <re xml:id="re_d2060e653" xml:lang="os-x-iron">
                        <lang/>
                        <form xml:id="form_d2060e657" type="lemma"><orth>army cæwy, wærmy næ</orth></form>
                        <sense xml:id="sense_d2060e660"><abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                                <q>в горсть вмещается, а в яму нет</q>
                            </abv:tr><abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                                <q>it fits in a handful, but not in a pit</q>
                            </abv:tr></sense>
                        <note type="comment" xml:lang="ru">. Такие слова, как <ref type="xr" target="#entry_dælarm"/> ‘под мышкой’, <ref type="xr" target="#entry_ræmbyn"/> ‘локоть’, <ref type="xr" target="#entry_ælmærīn"/> ‘локоть (мера)’, <ref type="xr" target="#entry_ærmæftaw"/> ‘переметная сумка’, указывают, что
                            <hi rendition="#rend_italic">arm</hi> значило не только ‘кисть’ (см. <bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#src_Сл."/></bibl>), но вся ‘рука’; ср. также у
                            <hi rendition="#rend_smallcaps">Ялгузидзе</hi> <mentioned xml:id="mentioned_d2060e684" xml:lang="os"><lang/>
                                <w>ærddæ</w>
                                <gloss><q>руки</q></gloss></mentioned> (<bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#src_Матфей"/><biblScope><hi rendition="#rend_italic">27</hi> 24</biblScope></bibl>).
                            Это же слово употреблялось в значении ‘оглобля’, как то свидетельствует
                            д. <ref type="xr" target="#entry_ar"/> ‘оглобля’, а также <ref type="xr" target="#entry_ardwan"/> ‘рашпиль’ и <ref type="xr" target="#entry_ærmbos"/> ‘гужовка’</note>
                        <note type="comment" xml:lang="en">. Such words as <ref type="xr" target="#entry_dælarm"/> ‘under one's arm’, <ref type="xr" target="#entry_ræmbyn"/> ‘elbow’, <ref type="xr" target="#entry_ælmærīn"/> ‘cubit’, <ref type="xr" target="#entry_ærmæftaw"/> ‘weather-vane’, indicate that <hi rendition="#rend_italic">arm</hi>
                            meant not only ‘hand’ (see <bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#src_Сл."/></bibl>), but the whole ‘arm’; cf. also <mentioned xml:id="mentioned_d2060e717" xml:lang="os"><lang/>
                                <w>ærddæ</w>
                                <gloss><q>hands</q></gloss></mentioned> by <hi rendition="#rend_smallcaps">Yalguzidze</hi>
                                    (<bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#src_Матфей"/><biblScope><hi rendition="#rend_italic">27</hi>
                                    24</biblScope></bibl>). The same word was used in the sense
                            ‘shaft’, as is proven by Digor <ref type="xr" target="#entry_ar"/>
                            ‘shaft’, and also <ref type="xr" target="#entry_ardwan"/> ‘rasp’ and
                                <ref type="xr" target="#entry_ærmbos"/> ‘tug’</note>
                    </re>
                </re>
                <abv:exampleGrp xml:id="exampleGrp_d2060e739">
                    <abv:example xml:id="example_d2060e741">
                        <quote>mæ fosæn syn dardton mæxī armæj cæxx</quote>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                            <q>моему скоту (предназначенному для калыма) я давал соль из собственной
                                руки</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                            <q>I gave salt from my own hand to my cattle (intended for kalym)</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#src_Коста"/><biblScope>60</biblScope></bibl>
                    </abv:example>
                    <abv:example xml:id="example_d2060e760">
                        <quote>ḱynʒ je ʽr(m)ttæ nyccaǧta</quote>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                            <q>невестка всплеснула руками</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                            <q>the daughter-in-law threw up her hands</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#src_ЮОПам."/><biblScope>I
                            102</biblScope></bibl>
                    </abv:example>
                    <abv:example xml:id="example_d2060e779">
                        <quote>pysyratæ je ʽrtty awwærsta</quote>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                            <q>он растер в руках крапиву</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                            <q>he rubbed nettles in his hands</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#src_F."/><biblScope>1957 III
                            26</biblScope></bibl>
                    </abv:example>
                    <abv:example xml:id="example_d2060e798">
                        <quote>īw bon k˳y wa, wæd dæ aftīd armæj æmæ gom rīwæj rarvītʒæn</quote>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                            <q>в один день он выгонит тебя с пустыми руками и голой грудью</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                            <q>one day he will kick you out empty-handed and bare-chested</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#src_Čerm."/><biblScope>107</biblScope></bibl>
                    </abv:example>
                    <abv:example xml:id="example_d2060e817">
                        <quote>kæd dæ army tʼæpænæj æxsyr cæwa, wæd ūj zon, æz ūdægas dæn; kæd dæ
                            army tʼæpænæj tūg ysqara, wæd ūj zon, ūdægas nal dæn</quote>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                            <q>если из твоей ладони будет идти молоко, то знай, что я жив; если из
                                твоей ладони выступит кровь, то знай, что меня уже нет в живых</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                            <q>if milk comes out of your palm, then know that I am alive; if blood
                                comes out of your palm, then know that I am no longer alive</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#src_ЮОПам."/><biblScope>III
                            16</biblScope></bibl>
                    </abv:example>
                    <abv:example xml:id="example_d2060e837" xml:lang="os-x-digor">
                        <usg><lang/></usg>
                        <quote>sæ armi kū neci baftudæj…</quote>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                            <q>когда им ничего не досталось в руки…</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                            <q>when they got nothing in their hands…</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#src_ОЭ"/><biblScope>I 94</biblScope></bibl>
                    </abv:example>
                    <abv:example xml:id="example_d2060e859" xml:lang="os-x-digor">
                        <usg><lang/></usg>
                        <quote>mʼarmi esti ku baftuja, wædta art nikkænʒinæn</quote>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                            <q>если раздобуду чего-нибудь, то разведу огонь</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                            <q>if I get something, I will start a fire</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#src_MSt."/><biblScope>10%l13%l</biblScope></bibl>
                    </abv:example>
                    <abv:example xml:id="example_d2060e881" xml:lang="os-x-digor">
                        <usg><lang/></usg>
                        <quote>baʒorun æ armi ne ʽftujuj</quote>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                            <q>позвать ей не удается („не дается в руки“)</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                            <q>she fails to call (‘not given in the hands’)</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#src_Bes._Ka_ke"/><biblScope>36</biblScope></bibl>
                    </abv:example>
                </abv:exampleGrp>
                <abv:exampleGrp xml:id="exampleGrp_d2060e904">
                    <abv:example xml:id="example_d2060e906">
                        <quote>zærond ʒonyǧ wyd… je ʽrttæn ma se ʽrdǵytæ xawdæj læwwydysty zæxxyl,
                            adæjmaǵy cænk˳yl kʼūxtaw</quote>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                            <q>сани были старые … только половинки оглобель лежали еще упавшие на
                                земле подобно обрубленным рукам человека</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                            <q>the sled was old … only the halves of the shaft lay still on the
                                ground like the severed hands of a man</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#src_F."/><biblScope>1957 I
                            8</biblScope></bibl>
                    </abv:example>
                </abv:exampleGrp>
                <note type="comment" xml:lang="ru">; о значении ‘оглобля’ см. также под <ref type="xr" target="#entry_ar"/> д.</note>
                <note type="comment" xml:lang="en">; see also Digor <ref type="xr" target="#entry_ar"/> about the meaning ‘shaft’</note>
                <etym xml:lang="ru">Как большинство анатомических терминов (см. <ref type="xr" target="#entry_kom"/> и др.), относится к старому иранскому фонду:
                        <mentioned corresp="#mentioned_d2060e1111" xml:id="mentioned_d2060e940" xml:lang="fa"><lang/>
                        <w>arm</w></mentioned> (в литературе не засвидетельствовано), <mentioned corresp="#mentioned_d2060e1116" xml:id="mentioned_d2060e945" xml:lang="zza"><lang/>
                        <w>ärmä</w>
                        <gloss><q>плечо</q></gloss></mentioned> (<bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#ref_KPF"/><biblScope xml:lang="ru">Abt. III, Bd. IV, стр.
                            280</biblScope></bibl>), <mentioned corresp="#mentioned_d2060e1129" xml:id="mentioned_d2060e958" xml:lang="wbl"><lang/>
                        <w>yurm</w>
                        <gloss><q>рука</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned corresp="#mentioned_d2060e1138" xml:id="mentioned_d2060e967" xml:lang="ydg"><lang/>
                        <w>yārmё</w></mentioned> (<bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#ref_Morgenstierne._IIFL"/><biblScope>II 59</biblScope></bibl>),
                        <mentioned corresp="#mentioned_d2060e1147" xml:id="mentioned_d2060e976" xml:lang="tly"><lang/>
                        <w>ām</w>
                        <gloss><q>плечо</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned corresp="#mentioned_d2060e1155" xml:id="mentioned_d2060e984" xml:lang="tly"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>предплечье</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned corresp="#mentioned_d2060e1161" xml:id="mentioned_d2060e990" xml:lang="sog"><lang/>
                        <w>*arm(’rm)</w></mentioned> в <mentioned corresp="#mentioned_d2060e1166" xml:id="mentioned_d2060e995" xml:lang="sog"><lang/>
                        <w>’ps’rm</w>
                        <gloss><q>имеющий связанные за спиной руки</q></gloss></mentioned>
                            (<bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#ref_Gramm._sogd."/><biblScope>II
                            90</biblScope></bibl>), <mentioned corresp="#mentioned_d2060e1179" xml:id="mentioned_d2060e1008" xml:lang="kho"><lang/>
                        <w>er-</w>
                        <gloss><q>рука</q></gloss></mentioned> (<bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#ref_BSOS"/><biblScope>X 585</biblScope></bibl>), <mentioned corresp="#mentioned_d2060e1191" xml:id="mentioned_d2060e1020" xml:lang="ae"><lang/>
                        <w>arəma-</w>
                        <gloss><q>рука</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned corresp="#mentioned_d2060e1199" xml:id="mentioned_d2060e1028" xml:lang="sa"><lang/>
                        <w>īrmá-</w>
                        <gloss><q>рука</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned corresp="#mentioned_d2060e1207" xml:id="mentioned_d2060e1036" xml:lang="xcl"><lang/>
                        <w>armukn</w>
                        <gloss><q>локоть</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned corresp="#mentioned_d2060e1216" xml:id="mentioned_d2060e1045" xml:lang="cu"><lang/>
                        <w n="0">рамо</w>
                        <gloss><q>плечо</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned corresp="#mentioned_d2060e1224" xml:id="mentioned_d2060e1054" xml:lang="prg"><lang/>
                        <w>irmo</w></mentioned>, <mentioned corresp="#mentioned_d2060e1229" xml:id="mentioned_d2060e1059" xml:lang="got"><lang/>
                        <w>arms</w></mentioned>, <mentioned corresp="#mentioned_d2060e1234" xml:id="mentioned_d2060e1064" xml:lang="de"><lang/>
                        <w>Arm</w>
                        <gloss><q>рука</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned corresp="#mentioned_d2060e1242" xml:id="mentioned_d2060e1072" xml:lang="la"><lang/>
                        <w>armus</w>
                        <gloss><q>лопатка</q></gloss></mentioned>. В значении ‘оглобля’ — <mentioned corresp="#mentioned_d2060e1250" xml:id="mentioned_d2060e1080" xml:lang="lt"><lang/>
                        <w>armai</w></mentioned>. Для истории осетинского языка представляет
                    интерес, что понятия ‘рука’, ‘нога’, ‘рот’ имеют наряду с иранскими
                    наименованиями (<hi rendition="#rend_italic">arm</hi>, <ref type="xr" target="#entry_kom"/>) параллельный ряд
                    неиранских, идущих из кавказского субстрата (<ref type="xr" target="#entry_ʒyx"/>), причем последние в самостоятельном употреблении почти вытеснили первые,
                    тогда как в старых сложных словах и сочетаниях встречаются почти исключительно
                    первые (иранские).%n<bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#ref_Миллер_Вс._ОЭ"/><biblScope>II 50</biblScope></bibl>; <bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#ref_Miller._Gr."/><biblScope>35</biblScope></bibl>. —
                            <bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#ref_Hübschmann._Oss."/><biblScope>24</biblScope></bibl>. — <bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#ref_ОЯФ_I"/><biblScope>17, 78, 117, 154,
                    197</biblScope></bibl>.</etym>
                <etym xml:lang="en">Like most anatomical terms (see <ref type="xr" target="#entry_kom"/> etc.), it belongs to the old Iranian stock: <mentioned corresp="#mentioned_d2060e940" xml:id="mentioned_d2060e1111" xml:lang="fa"><lang/>
                        <w>arm</w></mentioned> (not attested in literature), <mentioned corresp="#mentioned_d2060e945" xml:id="mentioned_d2060e1116" xml:lang="zza"><lang/>
                        <w>ärmä</w>
                        <gloss><q>shoulder</q></gloss></mentioned> (<bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#ref_KPF"/><biblScope xml:lang="en">Abt. III, Bd. IV, p.
                            280</biblScope></bibl>), <mentioned corresp="#mentioned_d2060e958" xml:id="mentioned_d2060e1129" xml:lang="wbl"><lang/>
                        <w>yurm</w>
                        <gloss><q>hand</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned corresp="#mentioned_d2060e967" xml:id="mentioned_d2060e1138" xml:lang="ydg"><lang/>
                        <w>yārmё</w></mentioned> (<bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#ref_Morgenstierne._IIFL"/><biblScope>II 59</biblScope></bibl>),
                        <mentioned corresp="#mentioned_d2060e976" xml:id="mentioned_d2060e1147" xml:lang="tly"><lang/>
                        <w>ām</w>
                        <gloss><q>shoulder</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned corresp="#mentioned_d2060e984" xml:id="mentioned_d2060e1155" xml:lang="tly"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>forearm</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned corresp="#mentioned_d2060e990" xml:id="mentioned_d2060e1161" xml:lang="sog"><lang/>
                        <w>*arm(’rm)</w></mentioned> in <mentioned corresp="#mentioned_d2060e995" xml:id="mentioned_d2060e1166" xml:lang="sog"><lang/>
                        <w>’ps’rm</w>
                        <gloss><q>with the hands tied behind</q></gloss></mentioned> (<bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#ref_Gramm._sogd."/><biblScope>II
                        90</biblScope></bibl>), <mentioned corresp="#mentioned_d2060e1008" xml:id="mentioned_d2060e1179" xml:lang="kho"><lang/>
                        <w>er-</w>
                        <gloss><q>hand</q></gloss></mentioned> (<bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#ref_BSOS"/><biblScope>X 585</biblScope></bibl>), <mentioned corresp="#mentioned_d2060e1020" xml:id="mentioned_d2060e1191" xml:lang="ae"><lang/>
                        <w>arəma-</w>
                        <gloss><q>hand</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned corresp="#mentioned_d2060e1028" xml:id="mentioned_d2060e1199" xml:lang="sa"><lang/>
                        <w>īrmá-</w>
                        <gloss><q>hand</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned corresp="#mentioned_d2060e1036" xml:id="mentioned_d2060e1207" xml:lang="xcl"><lang/>
                        <w>armukn</w>
                        <gloss><q>elbow</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned corresp="#mentioned_d2060e1045" xml:id="mentioned_d2060e1216" xml:lang="cu"><lang/>
                        <w>ramo</w>
                        <gloss><q>shoulder</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned corresp="#mentioned_d2060e1054" xml:id="mentioned_d2060e1224" xml:lang="prg"><lang/>
                        <w>irmo</w></mentioned>, <mentioned corresp="#mentioned_d2060e1059" xml:id="mentioned_d2060e1229" xml:lang="got"><lang/>
                        <w>arms</w></mentioned>, <mentioned corresp="#mentioned_d2060e1064" xml:id="mentioned_d2060e1234" xml:lang="de"><lang/>
                        <w>Arm</w>
                        <gloss><q>hand</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned corresp="#mentioned_d2060e1072" xml:id="mentioned_d2060e1242" xml:lang="la"><lang/>
                        <w>armus</w>
                        <gloss><q>shoulder-blade</q></gloss></mentioned>. As for the meaning
                    ‘shaft’, see <mentioned corresp="#mentioned_d2060e1080" xml:id="mentioned_d2060e1250" xml:lang="lt"><lang/>
                        <w>armai</w></mentioned>. For the history of Ossetic, it is of interest that
                    the concepts ‘hand’, ‘leg’, ‘mouth’, along with Iranian names (<hi rendition="#rend_italic">arm</hi>, <ref type="xr" target="#entry_kom"/>) have a parallel row of non-Iranian words
                    coming from the Caucasian substratum (<ref type="xr" target="#entry_ʒyx"/>), and
                    the latter words almost forced out the former words in independent use, while in
                    the old compound words and collocations there are almost exclusively the first
                    (Iranian) words.%n<bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#ref_Миллер_Вс._ОЭ"/><biblScope>II 50</biblScope></bibl>; <bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#ref_Miller._Gr."/><biblScope>35</biblScope></bibl>. —
                            <bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#ref_Hübschmann._Oss."/><biblScope>24</biblScope></bibl>. — <bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#ref_ОЯФ_I"/><biblScope>17, 78, 117, 154,
                    197</biblScope></bibl>.</etym>
